a
(a-0)^2+(a-0)^2=(|a|+2)^2
\implies 2a^2=a^2+4|a|+4\implies a^2-4|a|-4=0
a\ge0,a^2-4a-4=0, a=2\pm2\sqrt2
a\ge0,a=2+2\sqrt2
2a^2=(a+2)^2\implies \sqrt2a=a+2 
a>0,a+2>0
\implies(\sqrt2-1)a=2 \implies a=\frac 2{\sqrt2-1}=2(\sqrt2 +1)
(a-0)^2+(a-0)^2=(|a|-2)^2
a^2+4|a|-4=0
a>0,a^2+4a-4=0,a=-2\pm2\sqrt 2
a=2\sqrt2-2
2a^2=(a-2)^2
\implies \sqrt2a=a-2
a\ge 2
\implies (\sqrt2-1)a=-2\implies a=-\frac{2}{\sqrt 2-1}<0<2
\implies \sqrt2a=2-a
a< 2
\implies a(\sqrt2+1)=2\implies a=2(\sqrt 2-1)
